html
	head
		meta(charset='UTF-8')
		meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
		title Karol Świerczek - Portfolio
		link(rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css")
	body
		.menu.menu--transparent
			.menu__logo 
				p Karol Świerczek
			.menu__buttons
				.menu__button Home
				.menu__button About me
				.menu__button My portfolio
				.menu__button Offer
				.menu__button Contact
		.heading
			.heading__stack.float
				img(src='images/stack.svg' height='700px')
			.heading__about
				.heading__stack.float
					img(src='images/stack.svg' height='700px')
				.heading__content
					h1 Karol Świerczek
					p I'm 17 years old web developer from Cracow, and programming and creative ideas are my biggest passions. I love to transform whatever comes to my mind into more and more intriguing projects.
		.intro
			.intro__slot.revealOnScroll
				.intro__title About me
				p I've been programming since I was 12 years old, but I've been putting all my effort into it for a year. Every single day I'm learning how to create better and more advanced projects. I'm determined to improve and learn from my mistakes.
			.intro__slot.revealOnScroll
				.intro__title My workflow
				p Most of the time that I spend on programming I spend on learning javascript, Node.js, various frameworks and CSS, but recently I've also started to make android apps in Kotlin. I also like to make website designs (for instance like this portfolio) in Photoshop or Inkscape.
		.portfolio
			.portfolio__background.float
				img(src='images/background2.svg')
			.portfolio__title My portfolio
			#projects.portfolio__projects
				.project.revealOnScroll(v-for='(project, index) in projects' :class="{ 'project--primary': index < 3 }")
					.project__desc
						.project__photo(v-if='index < 3')
							img(:src='project.image')
						a.project__title(target='_blank' :href='project.url') {{project.title}}
						.project__about {{project.about}}
						.project__annotation {{project.annotation}}
			script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/vue/2.5.3/vue.min.js')
			script(src='js/index.js')